{"tid":11554,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"Strike the blood 噬血狂襲 OVA2 第1、2話","createTime":"2016-11-29T10:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T07:52:31.000Z","uid":34037,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e6a1a7e7dd9e4cfb18c9220bbfed7bcffbc54ca","tid":11554,"uid":34037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://u1.tdimg.com/6/148/5/_103102854625815706179759913604970996.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fu1.tdimg.com%2F6%2F148%2F5%2F_103102854625815706179759913604970996.jpg&h=b1382488&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【故事簡介】 <br />\n第四真祖&mdash;&mdash;是只在傳說中存在的世界最強之吸血鬼。而這位駕馭12眷獸、散播災難的幻之吸血鬼據說在日本出現了。為了監視並抹殺這位&ldquo;第四真祖&rdquo;，政府所屬的獅子王機關決定派遣攻魔師&ldquo;劍巫&rdquo;完成任務。而不知為何，被選為監視者的竟是一位見習&ldquo;劍巫&rdquo;少女&mdash;&mdash;姬柊雪菜。 <br />\n雪菜攜帶著對真祖用最強靈槍趕赴&ldquo;弦神市&rdquo;，而和她遭遇的&ldquo;第四真祖&rdquo;曉古城的真實身份卻是&mdash;&mdash;！學園幻想戰鬥劇將在浮於海上四季如夏的人工島上上演&mdash;&mdash;！ <br />\n<br />\n【STAFF】 <br />\n原作 - 三雲岳斗 <br />\n原作插畫 - 麻喵子 <br />\n監督 - 山本秀世 <br />\n監製 - 佐野隆雄 <br />\n動畫製作 - SILVER LINK.／CONNECT <br />\n<br />\n【CAST】 <br />\n曉古城：細谷佳正 <br />\n&amp;#23019;柊雪菜：種田梨沙 <br />\n藍羽淺蔥：瀨戶麻沙美 <br />\n曉&amp;#20970;沙：日高里菜 <br />\n矢瀨基樹：綠川光 <br />\n南宮那月：金元壽子 <br />\n阿斯塔魯特：井口裕香 <br />\n煌&amp;#22338;紗矢華：葉山郁美 <br />\n仙都木優麻：內山夕實 <br />\n<br />\nPV:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nkgKoBuUdW0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnkgKoBuUdW0&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=a7073d29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nkgKoBuUdW0</a><br />\n<br />\nOP:<a href=\"http://share.dmhy.org/topics/view/324775_131030_TV_OP_-_THE_320K.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshare.dmhy.org%2Ftopics%2Fview%2F324775_131030_TV_OP_-_THE_320K.html&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=177d5a13\" target=\"_blank\">http://share.dmhy.org/topics/view/324775_131030_TV_OP_-_THE_320K.html</